data.description: Stunning, Well Maintained 3 BR, 3 Full Bath Courtyard Home with Private & Intimate Pool on Screened Lanai. Separate Bedroom Casita with full Bath Ideal for Guests, Office, Adult Children or Parents for Personal Privacy. 12' Ceilings in Great Room area & Master Suite. Large Master BR with dual sinks and deep soaking tub. New Tile Roof 2020, New HVAC with Parts & Labor Warranty 2021. New Stainless LG kitchen Appliances 2022. Recently painted inside & out. Crown Molding in All rooms. Kids Pool Safety Fence. Granite Kitchen Countertops. Refaced Cabinets in 2022. New Glass Accent Backsplash. Luxury Vinyl Flooring in Kitchen, LR, DR, Main Bath, Laundry & Guest BR & New Carpet in Master Suite 2023. Pool Pump Motor 2023. 2 Car Garage with extra storage, Paver Driveway. See Sterling Oaks Brochure in Virtual Tour link. Clubhouse/Restaurant/Bar. Junior Olympic Pool & Spa. Full Bar/Luncheonette open 11-4:00. Kids Play Area. Fitness center, Sauna, Bocce & Pickle Ball courts all included in Dues. Optional Tennis membership with 12 Lighted Har-Tru Courts with on-site Pro. Minutes to Fine Dining, Shopping, SW Florida Airport & the many Stunning Beaches of SW Florida. No Flood Insurance Required.
